task.summary: Created toolbox package and added Matrix Creation
Created Entity class. Added functions to increase the position and rotation for an entity. Generated getters and setters.
Added a movable camera Configured the OpenGL depth tester.
Started adding support for dynamic lighting
Added a function to add object entitys faster.
Fixed the faster loading of objects. Added a TODO memo.
Optimised the Rendering Engine by creating a master Renderer.
Added terrain(aka sea for us) generation Added fog generation
Changed the default densiti and gradient.
Updated the OBJ file loader. Removed the old one.
Added camera movement. Added Ideas file.
Added multible light source support and attenuation support
Started the creation of the server.
Added Keyboard and mouse listeners. More gui stuff. New gameloop!
Created the multiplayer thread. Ran into some problems with running the game.
Added a Multiplayer Session IP and Port.
Font Rendering. But it is broken.... And it also took the game along with him to the broken land.
Cleaned up Camera class from commented functions
